        "subtitle": "",
        "title": "How it actually started",
        "heading_size": "h2",
        "text": "<p>Most &ldquo;fermented&rdquo; food today isn't fermented. It's: pasteurised, vinegar-based, built for shelf life.</p>",
        "align_text": "left",
        "image_width": "50",
        "layout": "right",
        "divider": false,
        "top_padding": true,
        "bottom_padding": true
      }
    },
